items.title: Nightclub Fire Kills at Least 59 in North Macedonia
items.description: The tragedy occurred after fireworks set the club’s roof on fire during a pop concert, the country’s interior minister said.

items.title: Ukraine Retreats From Most of Russia’s Kursk Region
items.description: The daring campaign Ukraine launched last summer to seize and occupy Russian territory appears to be nearing an end.

items.title: Children Try to Cheer Pope Francis During His Hospital Stay
items.description: Dozens of young people gathered under the pontiff’s windows at the Gemelli hospital to offer wishes for a quick recovery.

items.title: East African Housekeepers Face Rape, Assault and Death in Saudi Arabia
items.description: East African leaders and Saudi royals are among those profiting off a lucrative, deadly trade in domestic workers.
